e x1=\"3\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></nav></div></div><!--$?--><template id=\"B:0\"></template><main class=\"relative z-[3] mx-auto w-full max-w-[1180px] px-[22px] pt-28 pb-16 sm:pt-32\"></main><!--/$--><footer class=\"relative z-[3] flex justify-center px-[22px] pt-[30px] pb-11\"><div class=\"flex w-full max-w-[1180px] flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-[18px] sm:px-[22px]\" style=\"border-radius:20px;background:var(--glass-bg);background-image:var(--glass-tint);backdrop-filter:blur(var(--glass-blur)) saturate(180%);border:1px solid var(--glass-brd);box-shadow:inset 0 1px 0 var(--glass-hi)\"><span class=\"text-[13px]\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">© 2026 Daffa Ilham Restupratama</span><span class=\"mono text-[11px]\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Data · Business · Finance · Maps · Walking Tours</span></div></footer></div><script>requestAnimationFrame(function(){$RT=performance.now()});</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0a1gboz92241g.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><div hidden id=\"S:0\"><main class=\"relative z-[3] mx-auto w-full max-w-[1180px] px-[22px] pt-28 pb-16 sm:pt-32\"><header class=\"max-w-[720px]\"><h1 class=\"font-bold\" style=\"font-size:clamp(30px,4.5vw,50px);line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.03em\">City Walking Tours with Daffa</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-[16px]\" style=\"line-height:1.62;color:var(--ink-dim)\">Explore Indonesian cities through public transport, local history, food, and hidden stories.</p></header><div class=\"mt-7 max-w-[760px]\"><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">My city tours are designed for travelers who want to understand a place beyond typical tourist stops. I focus on walking routes, public transport, local food, city history, and hidden gems that reveal how people actually experience the city.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">The tours currently focus on Jakarta, Bogor, Tangerang, and Yogyakarta. Some routes are urban and history-based, while others explore nature destinations such as waterfalls around Bogor.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">Each route can be adjusted based on your interests, walking comfort, schedule, and preferred pace.</p></div><div class=\"mt-7 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/62XXXXXXXXXXX\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"btn-gradient gap-2 px-[21px] py-3 text-[14.5px]\">Ask for a Custom Tour<svg width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></a><span class=\"max-w-[36ch] text-[13px]\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Send a message to discuss route, schedule, group size, and price.</span></div><section class=\"glass-card mt-10 p-6 sm:p-8\" style=\"border-radius:22px\"><div class=\"relative z-[2]\"><div><h3 class=\"text-[15px] font-semibold\" style=\"letter-spacing:-0.01em\">Why tour with me</h3><ul class=\"mt-2.5 flex flex-col gap-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>Story-based tours that connect places with context, not just photo stops.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>Public transport-friendly routes for a more grounded city experience.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>Flexible pacing for solo travelers, students, and small groups.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>Local food, history, and hidden gems blended into one route.</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>Clear communication in Indonesian and English.</li></ul></div></div></section><section class=\"mt-12\"><h2 class=\"mb-[22px] font-bold\" style=\"font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,34px);letter-spacing:-0.03em\">Featured tours</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-[18px] md:grid-cols-2\"><div data-tilt=\"true\" class=\"glass-card flex flex-col gap-4 p-[15px] sm:flex-row\"><div class=\"relative z-[2] aspect-[16/9] w-full shrink-0 sm:aspect-auto sm:w-[150px] sm:min-h-[210px]\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-radius:15px\"><img alt=\"Kota tua jakarta\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://cms.daffa.me/uploads/asyiknya_berwisata_di_kota_tua_jakarta_ini_sederet_pilihan_destinasinya_Bd76x_Or_Dum_44262bf73e.jpg\"/></div><div class=\"relative z-[2] flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-2.5\"><h3 class=\"m-0 text-lg font-bold\" style=\"letter-spacing:-0.025em\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-(--accent-ink)\" href=\"/tours/jakarta-public-transport-old-city-walking-tour\">Jakarta Public Transport &amp; Old City Walking Tour</a></h3><span class=\"flex shrink-0 flex-col items-end px-3 py-2\" style=\"border-radius:14px;back